

Over view:
	- CodeIgniter is an Application Framework
	- Free
	- Light Weight
	- Fast	
	- Uses M-V-C
	- Generates Clean URLs
	- Packs a Punch
	- is Extensible
	- Does Not Require a Template Engine
	- is Thoroughly Documented
	- has a Friendly Community of Users
	
	
Feature:
	- Model-View-Controller Based System
    - Extremely Light Weight
    - Full Featured database classes with support for several platforms.
    - Query Builder Database Support
    - Form and Data Validation
    - Security and XSS Filtering
    - Session Management
    - Email Sending Class. Supports Attachments, HTML/Text email, multiple protocols (sendmail, SMTP, and Mail) and more.
    - Image Manipulation Library (cropping, resizing, rotating, etc.). Supports GD, ImageMagick, and NetPBM
    - File Uploading Class
    - FTP Class
    - Localization
    - Pagination
    - Data Encryption
    - Benchmarking
    - Full Page Caching
    - Error Logging
    - Application Profiling
    - Calendaring Class
    - User Agent Class
    - Zip Encoding Class
    - Template Engine Class
    - Trackback Class
    - XML-RPC Library
    - Unit Testing Class
    - Search-engine Friendly URLs
    - Flexible URI Routing
    - Support for Hooks and Class Extensions
    - Large library of “helper” functions


-- Tạm dịch -- 

Tổng quan: 
	- CodeIgniter là một Application Framework (tạm dịch: khung xương ứng dụng)
	- Hoàn toàn miễn phí
	- Nhẹ
	- Nhanh
	- Sử dụng M-V-C (Model-View-Controler)
		+ M-V-C là một cách tiếp cận phần mềm tách riêng phần sử lý logic ra khỏi phần hiển thị (liên kết băng một trình điều khiển)
	- Phát sinh những địa chỉ web "sạch sẽ"
	- Packs a Punch
	- is Extensible
	- Does Not Require a Template Engine
	- is Thoroughly Documented
	- has a Friendly Community of Users
